of my personal favorites.

134
00:09:08,214 --> 00:09:09,818
Now, before you all
start groaning

135
00:09:10,049 --> 00:09:12,859
about how you ended up
with such a mean teacher,

136
00:09:13,119 --> 00:09:16,589
