inside with you?

173
00:11:36,462 --> 00:11:37,736
Conflict.

174
00:11:37,963 --> 00:11:39,237
Exactly.

175
00:11:39,465 --> 00:11:41,103
Man versus himself.

176
00:11:41,333 --> 00:11:42,835
Ah.

177
00:11:52,311 --> 00:11:55,849
